    <description>[url]https://store.steampowered.com[/url]

Like Santa, the Steam Holiday Sale only comes once a year. Unlike Santa tho, the Steam Holiday Sale has the real gifts that keep on giving.

All in all, it&#39;s all to make Gabe Newell even more stinking rich while he&#39;s too busy not making HL3.

Anyway, what have you bought so far and what are you waiting to buy at ridiculously low prices?

So far I&#39;ve bought Lost Planet 1&amp;2 and Metal Gear Rising. I&#39;m also hoping to score some cheap Bioshock Infinite DLC action and reluctantly mulling over if I should or not buy Batman Arkham Origins. Maybe I&#39;ll get Don&#39;t Starve as well.

Decisions, decisions...</description>
    
